title: Paul McCartney: Got Back - Live at River Plate Stadium
overview: Live transmission of Paul McCartney's Buenos Aires show show on October 5th, 2024.  As one of the most iconic and successful musicians of all time, McCartney boasts an unparalleled discography. With hits like 'Hey Jude', 'Live and Let Die', 'Band on the Run', and 'Let It Be', witnessing Paul McCartney live is a dream come true for music enthusiasts. Get ready for an unforgettable rock concert featuring the best moments from six decades of music, with a setlist spanning his solo career, Wings, and, of course, The Beatles, soundtrack of many people's lives.
